4.2 VULNERABILITY OVERVIEW
4.2.1    UNQUOTED SEARCH PATH OR ELEMENT CWE-428
--------- Begin Update K Part 2 of 2 ---------
The affected product is vulnerable due to a common component of the affected applications that regularly calls a helper binary with SYSTEM privileges while the call path is not quoted. This could allow a local unauthorized user to execute arbitrary code with SYSTEM privileges.CVE-2020-7580 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 8.8 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (AV:L/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H).
--------- End Update K Part 2 of 2 ---------
